==Text==
Dear {{MC|m=Mr.|f=Miss}} (Trailblazer),

<div align="center">When the cold wind brings the first drifting snow,<br />
we step into the muddy wilderness.<br />
Gathering the dying petals,<br />
we let their withered glory rest in the traveler's flower crown.

From footprints traveling back and forth, paths are woven.<br />
Never had I imagined that one day I would wear a flower crown.<br />
Leave this snowy realm, cross that boundary dawn and dusk, between life and death.<br />
Journey to a world still warm with life,<br />
and smile while embracing others.

Before your departure, take this flower crown with you.<br />
It has accompanied me through endless paths, across the shores of darkness.<br />
Chase the end of the west wind, and witness the world's rebirth.

May those flowers, like dancing butterflies,<br />
rest upon your brow when you're weary.<br />
May life's gentle warmth always stay by your side.


Castorice</div>

